title: Providing for the adoption of the Rules of the Senate for a certain period of time
fulltext:
SENATE  RESOLUTION providing for the adoption of the Rules of the Senate
for a certain period of time

RESOLVED, That the Rules of the Senate, as adopted  pursuant  to  Senate
Resolution  7,  on January 5, 2011, are hereby adopted for the period of
January 5, 2011 through February 1, 2011.
